## A4. REGRESSION CHECK PROMPT (Jalankan setelah setiap 3-5 task selesai)

```
REGRESSION CHECK. Stop semua development. Run checks:

STEP 1 - COMPILE CHECK:
- npx tsc --noEmit
- Report: jumlah errors. Jika > 0, list semua dan FIX sebelum lanjut.

STEP 2 - BOOT CHECK:
- npx expo start
- App harus boot tanpa crash. Report: YES/NO.

STEP 3 - IMPORT CHECK:
- Scan semua file .ts/.tsx yang ada.
- Pastikan semua import paths resolve ke file yang exist.
- Report: jumlah broken imports.

STEP 4 - PREVIOUS PHASE CHECK:
- Untuk setiap phase yang sudah DONE, verify key features masih jalan:
  - Phase 0: Auth flow, onboarding, tab navigation, role switching
  - Phase 1: Warga CRUD, laporan share, consumer web portal
  - Phase 2: Lapak pedagang, catat penjualan, katalog
  - Phase 3: Sewa properti, tenant billing, contract
  - Phase 4: Laundry/guru/jasa modes, consumer real-time
  - Phase 5: Hajat undangan, RSVP, amplop
  - (Check only phases that are DONE)

STEP 5 - FIX:
- Fix ALL errors found in steps 1-4.
- Untuk setiap fix, VERIFY bahwa fix tersebut tidak break hal lain.
- Update MODIFICATIONS LOG di PROGRESS.md.

Report format:
"REGRESSION CHECK [date]:
- Compile: [X] errors -> [fixed/pending]
- Boot: [YES/NO]
- Imports: [X] broken -> [fixed/pending]
- Phase [N] features: [OK/FAIL - detail]
- Fixes applied: [list]
- Confidence level: [HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW]"
```

